Description:
    The limewire_plugin generator creates a skeleton plugin for use with
    Remote Limewire.  

    The Limewire 'plugin' is not a rails plugin but more like a Rails Engine.  
    It contains models, controllers, helpers, views, and assets. It is
    intended to be the distribution system for miniature apps that run
    on top of Limewire.

Example:
    ./script/generate limewire_plugin Peers index show widget
        ...
        create  plugins/peers/controllers/
        create  plugins/peers/helpers/
        create  plugins/peers/views/peers
        create  plugins/peers/test/functional/
        create  plugins/peers/controllers/peers_controller.rb
        create  plugins/peers/test/functional/peers_controller_test.rb
        create  plugins/peers/helpers/peers_helper.rb
        create  plugins/peers/routes.rb
        create  plugins/peers/views/peers/index.html.erb
        create  plugins/peers/views/peers/show.html.erb
        create  plugins/peers/views/peers/widget.html.erb

Your plugin will be available immediately at /[plugin_name]